    Scope and Contents
These records include: University Anthem Committee correspondence and sheet music, Compliance Report (6/75), Annual Reports, promotional calendars and the Foundation publications "Horizons" (10-90, 2/91, 7/91) and "Investing in Illinois" (Spring, 1996).
Correspondence included: letters regarding various donations, proposed changes in by-laws, list of contributors and proposed membership list.
Financial information includes the following: monthly account statements, Reports of the Treasurer and letters to potential donors regarding the fund drive of 9/73.  
  
